{"tid":517424,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"請珍惜阿Mag林欣彤","createTime":"2018-01-02T09:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T14:16:05.000Z","uid":120805,"like":56,"dislike":108,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"fdfbed890a5008a2c7c32fed20f6cdb9d0c9ccfc","tid":517424,"uid":120805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T09:57:29.000Z","msg":"一直都有聽開阿mag, 近兩三年聲勢真係沉咗好多, 佢好似俾人忽略咗咁, 同期巨聲幫中唔好講許廷鏗, 連當日手下敗仗嘅坤哥同刀削面都開始有爬頭之勢。<br />\n<br />\n早幾日响youtube聽佢cover首&lt;那裡只得我共你&gt;, 覺得唱得真係好好聽, 再搵返幾段佢近期唱嘅live片段, 真心覺得佢唱功其實真係屌打90%本地女歌手, 比起之前進步咗唔少, 特別分享下, 希望支持本地音樂嘅可以支持吓阿mag...<br />\n<br />\n那裡只得我共你cover<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/q8VMHax65JI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fq8VMHax65JI&d=nZRNgdHY6xtRP5JeSkPu05ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=70fc30d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/q8VMHax65JI</a><br />\n<br />\n&lt;一人旅行團+奇怪+浮誇+懸崖花&gt;Live<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CjQ2Mi394xA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCjQ2Mi394xA&d=nZRNgdHY6xtRP5JeSkPu05ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=2512b68a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CjQ2Mi394xA</a><br />\n<br />\n保良show同陳潔靈pk<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ClQ0RzQfC84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FClQ0RzQfC84&d=nZRNgdHY6xtRP5JeSkPu05ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=94706a34\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ClQ0RzQfC84</a><br />\n<br />\n特別推薦第二段片一連四首的live, 四首歌剛柔並重, 特別係唱浮誇, 真係超正, 係聽過嘅女版入面真係數一數二<br />\n<br />\n其實香港樂壇入面仲有唔少新一輩唱得之人, 阿Mag前路係比教崎嶇嘅一個, 希望大家花少少時間睇下上面幾段片支持吓阿Mag...<br />\n<br />\n請珍惜林欣彤。"},{"pid":"fbc05aadd750f9a9d013ef3a862c7aaf50c11599","tid":517424,"uid":63450,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T09:58:05.000Z","msg":"好行夾唔送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39de57813e6a06eff68425a351440bfe0e1f7b3","tid":517424,"uid":71560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T09:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd697aeb4c100ab234a52b011bce716e8e4d7510","tid":517424,"uid":85819,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"beb8a5f251341d319c171ba57374fb71f797ada1","tid":517424,"uid":133651,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:04:52.000Z","msg":"呢排咁多打手post"},{"pid":"5ca5f71a34c3eb1e748337f99406a18962e69aec","tid":517424,"uid":120805,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:09:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢排咁多打手post</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絕對唔係打手....只係噚晚睇叱吒, 見阿mag冇出席, 諗返起佢兩年前都有歌入到10大...有少少感慨所以出post啫<br />\n<br />\n如果影響到各位巴絲, 對唔住"},{"pid":"d212a6396cf2b0277b4736a2d47f3c17501edef3","tid":517424,"uid":58068,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:13:32.000Z","msg":"收皮"},{"pid":"9bf7ace907cbcbaf7a6346099ea8e6068968eaac","tid":517424,"uid":147789,"like":21,"dislike":8,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:14:50.000Z","msg":"其實佢唱歌唔差 點解咁多人唔鍾意？<br />\n真心想知"},{"pid":"6d35bc500335ec84728d641af48487a535198eb6","tid":517424,"uid":85819,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:17:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56fcff50223e469b5bde24182a32df005aa0daa5","tid":517424,"uid":161472,"like":23,"dislike":4,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:19:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c92d44ba4914f26073df1889156509fa6450eb66","tid":517424,"uid":123774,"like":15,"dislike":7,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:22:20.000Z","msg":"一拍埋gem即收皮"},{"pid":"c9774d099a92e09e30fa5c52ce783028a02f9783","tid":517424,"uid":129221,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:31:33.000Z","msg":"首首歌都係個把死人聲...<br />\n由巨星幫到而家都一成不變 點撐佢"},{"pid":"24106aa3bba04ff367809dfb668bacbb8bca4625","tid":517424,"uid":120805,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:32:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一拍埋gem即收皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁認真講, 歌藝上阿gem真係高佢一班, 但阿mag比起其他同一輩女歌手, 已經贏好多人啦<br />\n<br />\n講live, 我覺得新一輩只有阿gem同gin lee可以話好過同穩過mag....."},{"pid":"abee62f571ddd193e961e7a9b330cc9ae9a75c86","tid":517424,"uid":120805,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:39:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首首歌都係個把死人聲...<br />\n由巨星幫到而家都一成不變 點撐佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打如果有少少時間可以睇下上面片段, 其實我真心覺得佢比以前進步咗好多<br />\n<br />\n好多人一講阿mag就話佢嗌歌, 鼻音好重, 咬字唔清晰, 但如果你有時間聽下, 佢呢d問題真係改善左, 特別係咬字"},{"pid":"7d9bdaf64cf3dce1d2909457cf43c92c50403a4f","tid":517424,"uid":127571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:45:49.000Z","msg":"唱歌係有技巧，係高班，但係聽佢唱既歌始終入唔到心，感染唔到我。佢好多歌聽幾次就厭，因為佢把聲真係打入唔到我個心。我聽音樂就係咁單純，無感覺就係無感覺。希望樓主可以搵到其他知音人啦。"},{"pid":"905f35494df8a7efd64a997ed4ec4f6744d04028","tid":517424,"uid":52911,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:47:41.000Z","msg":"佢把聲有特色 但好撚難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8bc6453fea57c5fb9ef8ac5cddf4aa63b3f657","tid":517424,"uid":5929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:51:27.000Z","msg":"唔知點解覺得佢把聲好怪<br />\n但又唔算好難聽"},{"pid":"67eb3a03089125641421e553aebef75fc7a30554","tid":517424,"uid":1515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:52:41.000Z","msg":"屌咁講唔通AGA嗰啲叫有技巧好聽咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79acc1ef79754f951763205c8a1e1eedcbef28d7","tid":517424,"uid":7606,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:57:41.000Z","msg":"唱歌好似含住條撚咁 聽到好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2352e0e0ee861ee50219fa288d2da16290ed0fa9","tid":517424,"uid":120805,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:59:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唱歌係有技巧，係高班，但係聽佢唱既歌始終入唔到心，感染唔到我。佢好多歌聽幾次就厭，因為佢把聲真係打入唔到我個心。我聽音樂就係咁單純，無感覺就係無感覺。希望樓主可以搵到其他知音人啦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我都好同意, 聽歌真係好個人好講主觀感覺嘅。好似容祖兒都有人話佢唱到入晒心, 亦有人話佢賣弄歌藝冇感情, 亦正如有人會覺得aga 吳若希 hana唱得好...<br />\n<br />\n其實噚晚一路睇叱吒一路追post, 真係幾感慨, 唔同歌星出現都總有一大班人出嚟否定佢地, 點解唔可以單純啲去講音樂...<br />\n<br />\n我唔否認有啲歌星真係有自己問題或者不足, 不過只係想講, 香港廣東歌樂壇真係越嚟越衰落, 好多大牌都走返大陸搵食懶得理香港呢個市場, 不過其實都真係仲有唔少有心人選擇响香港默默耕耘, 就算唔支持, 都唔好加多兩腳....<br />\n<br />\n我知我講多咗, 請見諒...."},{"pid":"3e5ee70b6e26999b43b964ea1f9f743c84ce1370","tid":517424,"uid":133341,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/tvb4life/1427276275-1334609727.jpg?v=1427276725\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Ftvb4life%2F1427276275-1334609727.jpg%3Fv%3D1427276725&h=73a92f6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adab7db9b770970e82163d71ccdd560605a4aa80","tid":517424,"uid":33899,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:03:00.000Z","msg":"個死人唱腔好撚難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首首歌都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46f062ce5fe70225961685b1fa3c3ea46924c90","tid":517424,"uid":52132,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:06:06.000Z","msg":"識貨"},{"pid":"4a7f2d3c088a3916910c4baf139114a1f556a7e3","tid":517424,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ca5f71a34c3eb1e748337f99406a18962e69aec","tid":517424,"uid":120805,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:09:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢排咁多打手post</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絕對唔係打手....只係噚晚睇叱吒, 見阿mag冇出席, 諗返起佢兩年前都有歌入到10大...有少少感慨所以出post啫<br />\n<br />\n如果影響到各位巴絲, 對唔